# Keep the web Docker image build context lean and — critically — keep the
# monorepo additions (Expo mobile app, shared core package) OUT of the web
# image build. The Dockerfile runs `npm install` from package.json before
# `COPY . .`; because the workspace globs in package.json match nothing
# inside the Docker context, the web image builds exactly as it did before
# the monorepo split. When Phase 1 makes the web app depend on
# @wealthai/core, remove `packages` from this list and reorder the
# Dockerfile COPY steps deliberately.
node_modules
dist
apps
packages
.git
.github
.playwright-mcp
e2e/screenshots
test-results
ios
*.log
